PalettePal Privacy Policy
PalettePal ("we", "our", "us") values your privacy. This Privacy Policy informs you about how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our app that helps generate colors.
PalettePal does not collect or store any personal information from users on their devices.
Since we do not collect any personal information, we do not use or share your personal information in any way.
We take the security of your data seriously. As no personal data is collected, there is no risk of data breaches or misuse of your information.
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any updates.
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
tunds@minimaapps.co.uk
.
This Privacy Policy is effective as of 12/07/2024.